      <title>月球着陆器制造商直观机器超出销售预期</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-21/moon-lander-maker-intuitive-machines-beats-sales-expectations</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Intuitive Machines Inc.上季度的销售预期超过了华尔街的预期，这对最近因在月球上登陆航天器而声名鹊起的公司来说是又一提振。]]></description>
